DateTime::Locale::nb_SJ(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::nb_SJ(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::nb_SJ - Locale data examples for the Norwegian Bokmål Svalbard & Jan Mayen (nb-SJ) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Norwegian Bokmål Svalbard & Jan Mayen locale.

  mandag
  tirsdag
  onsdag
  torsdag
  fredag
  lørdag
  søndag

  man.
  tir.
  ons.
  tor.
  fre.
  lør.
  søn.

  O
  T
  F
  L
  S

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = tirsdag 5. februar 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = fredag 22. desember 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = lørdag 15. september -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. februar 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. desember 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. september -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. feb. 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. des. 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. sep. -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05.02.2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22.12.1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15.09.-10

Time Formats

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 09:05:02 UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04:44:23 UTC

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 18:30:30 UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 09:05:02 UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04:44:23 UTC

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 18:30:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 09:05:02
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04:44:23

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 18:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 09:05
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04:44

Datetime Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = tirsdag 5. februar 2008 18:30:30 UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = fredag 22. desember 1995 09:05:02 UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = lørdag 15. september -10 04:44:23 UTC

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. februar 2008 kl. 18:30:30 UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. desember 1995 kl. 09:05:02 UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. september -10 kl. 04:44:23 UTC

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. feb. 2008, 18:30:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. des. 1995, 09:05:02
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. sep. -10, 04:44:23

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05.02.2008, 18:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22.12.1995, 09:05
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15.09.-10, 04:44
